{
  "stem": "17301.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And the only place, the only way you were able to sleep, if you sat down, and you-- and you pulled up your-- your legs to your chin and sleep that way, because you could not stretch out and go to sleep.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And that was another camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was-- I don't know whether they had-- they didn't have a crematorium there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But it was not of the best of camps to start with.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We was-- as it happened in-- in-- not too many.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the ones that I knew, it was only my mother and my sister and one other person that I knew that ended up, because they selected in-- in Ravensbruck, they selected people randomly.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I didn't know where the other people went, because they told us this is where you gonna to sleep.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they taken the other ones in-- in different barracks, in different parts of Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I don't know what happened to them from then on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I know, you know, when-- when they lined us up, they lined us up with people that were already in Ravensbruck for a while.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because whoever came with us didn't look familiar to us at all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It wasn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we were still very lucky to be with my mother and my sister.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that's-- we ended up in-- in Neustadt-Glewe with my mother and my sister and one other person that I know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were-- there were the four of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were liberated--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--from Neustadt-Glewe, we were liberated May 3rd of that year.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we ended up-- when we got to Neustadt-Glewe, they told us we're going to be working, which was fine.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I felt, you know, working is OK.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were all of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
